data.name: aboutTextLbl.Text
data.value:
Welcome to Food Detective, an app dedicated to raising awareness about harmful food additives and encouraging clean eating.
Additives are substances “added to food to maintain or improve[its] safety, freshness, taste, texture, or appearance” (“Food Additives”). By failing to properly regulate what enters our food supply, the Food and Drug Administration has exposed us to food that raises risks of health issues, such as cancer and heart disease (Lassalle).
To protect your right to safe food, please donate to the Center for Food Safety by clicking on “Donate” at the top right. Thank you.
